  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-642aaad0-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-67cbcb57177a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642aaacf-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-61c423cdc0ac\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642aaacd-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-d9bb555756a3\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2026-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-59d5db2925f4\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b2024-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-57473128ab94\">이수한의원 문원장입니다 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b202b-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-e3d6cfb349ff\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b202a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-3be2c01b9ef8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b202f-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-7b821b7c90d5\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b202e-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-276e05c5338a\">작년부터 등산을 다시 시작해서 겨울내내 산을 참 많이도 다녔습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2033-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-bb593a076503\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b2032-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-0dd4882d857f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2037-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-d147ca87b459\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b2036-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-4f0003aca5a9\">20대 때는 한라산 지리산 등 큰 산을 겁도 없이 많이 다녔었어요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b203b-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-d5ce3f469401\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b203a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-992727b0af6d\">산속에서 야영이 허용되던 시절. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b203f-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-2f36787968f5\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b203c-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-bfd2fc35c35e\">지리산에서 텐트치고 끓여먹던 라면.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2043-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-4503b8966241\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b2042-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-e5141913d3a8\">치악산에서 구워먹던 삼겹살. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2048-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-97567b9c62be\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b2046-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-5f210acb65dd\">한라산에서 사먹었던 사발면.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b204c-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-5f2bc4cd31b5\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b204a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-6b392dece0ee\">힘든 산행 후 성취감과 함께 먹던 음식들은, 그게 뭐든 너무나 맛있었어요</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2050-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-5f4c845d8dc9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b204e-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-db650b352d62\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2055-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-47b55da62f7d\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b2052-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-fd8e809d702a\">그 후 한참을 등산과 멀어졌다가 작년부터 등산화, 등산복 등 간단한 장비들을 구비하고 가을산행, 겨울산행을 했더랬죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2059-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-a50cb44b10ae\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b2057-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-07fea89bca85\">다리도 아프고, 체력도 부족했지만 재밌었습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b205d-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-d3824b3e8532\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b205b-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-1daca553df0b\">시간이 부족해서 가고싶은 유명한 산을 가지 못하는게 아쉬웠지만 가까이 있는 작은 산이라도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2061-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-776a7639afba\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b205f-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-0fa282ea8043\">‘산’이란 자체가 참 좋았습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2065-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-9352882f5f3b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b2064-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-e34322fc6b77\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2067-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-db5e2366ebb5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b2066-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-dd9f3dc417a7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b206a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-a546d1fc8023\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b2068-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-49c31fa3ead1\">2022년 오미크론 대유행이 시작되면서 등산도 뜸해졌습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b206f-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-bf54fe690e6a\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b206e-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-6b756f6915ba\">산에는 마스크 없이 거친 숨을 쉬는 분들이 많아서, 조심하느라 안갔습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2073-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-7f7315c4c01f\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b2072-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-416eb9a37331\">이런저런 일들로 시간이 여의치 않기도 했어요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2079-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-a5ccf519345a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b2078-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-092b2be27805\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b207b-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-7f0a16e691e7\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b207a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-0d8eaed7df1d\">등산을 한참 재미붙여 할 때, 하체 근력 향상을 위해서 러닝을 병행하기 시작했죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b207f-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-671809a565bd\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b207e-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-87da589e414e\">30분 쉬지 않고 달리는걸 목표로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2083-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-2151f26572ab\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b2082-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-cdc9750ebd5c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2087-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-bb25c5c31e55\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b2086-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-c74213419f74\">등산을 못가게되니 러닝이 주된 운동이 되버렸어요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b208b-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-91f159d18901\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b208a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-157727a6d7c9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b208d-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-5d31f03f7145\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b208c-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-bf7eea694da8\">Runday 라는 어플을 깔고, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2091-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-6515ba723834\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b2090-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-89a7657e13d3\">30분 달리기 트레이닝을 시작한지 벌써 몇 달이 지났습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b2097-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-d9ad7fb79402\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b2096-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-032e153b38ed\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b209a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-9d50527ac08c\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b2098-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-7574e6efb589\">처음에는 1-2분 달린 후 걷기. 그리고 다시 달리기를 반복하는 것부터 시작했죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b209d-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-df29aec3d3fa\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b209c-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-5db1a928aa47\">2분, 3분 달리는게 이렇게 힘들다니!!! 말도 안돼!!! </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46b1-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-c1aadbbd35ce\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46b0-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-25153a49400e\">그렇게 점차 늘려가면서 달린 시간이 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46b7-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-ad668dce896a\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46b4-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-855d296ae633\">어플 기록상 벌써 8주차 2번째 달리기까지 왔습니다. (매 주 3회 달리기니까 23회 달린거죠)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a55d3211-aba0-4f07-8bf1-e7a3327c0f34\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-9067931d-9dea-46eb-998e-4cd0e6cd590b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0a0e375b-9ee0-406c-bb8b-00a36d02e058\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0a0e375b-9ee0-406c-bb8b-00a36d02e058\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4bcb18853731288f.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1440\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3040\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4bcb18853731288f.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4bcb18853731288f.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"1055\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-162eb7fc-c888-4a0a-90eb-2d9f00199e69\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-751d3414-d6a4-46e1-b939-5a5dd4b17a72\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-76330385-23e7-4726-8a6b-b90a1a2dd6f3\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46b9-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-19910fc048fa\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46b8-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-53ef00a6a89a\">8주차 3번째 달리기가 트레이닝의 끝입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46bf-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-97f0ce433e20\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b46be-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-0f7735e6e85b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46c3-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-5f1ade6be196\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46c2-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-116eb2fc7b4b\">오늘은 25분을 쉬지 않고 달렸습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46c7-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-91de4e3e9149\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46c6-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-57f5fdbbfbd4\">기록을 보니 4km를 쉬지 않고 달렸네요</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a8a548e-6309-49c7-a067-607c1649a8c9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4a8a548e-6309-49c7-a067-607c1649a8c9\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/84abc6b6187f09f2.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1440\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3040\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/84abc6b6187f09f2.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/84abc6b6187f09f2.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"1055\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3568d675-14d5-4734-8038-52a8471aed9b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46cd-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-a117ce9e6457\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46cc-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-ab2c7c4c744d\">2-3일 후..  8주차 3번째, 마지막 트레이닝인 30분 달리기를 해야합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46d1-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-bdf5bf0c0ef6\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46d0-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-af92708ec6f2\">25분 달리기를 완주한 후, 25분 달리기를 성공했다는 기쁨과 함께</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46d7-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-0db7d3c6d2b9\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46d6-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-8b62333bf52d\">30분 달리기에 대한 기대와 욕심이 생깁니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46db-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-d921d5e3090b\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46da-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-b7aadfa80422\">해낼 수 있다는 자기세뇌를 반복하면서 30분 달리기를 해낼겁니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46df-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-55efc852520b\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46de-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-318cbe42f41d\">그러기 위해서 다리 마사지, 지압, 찜질, 침치료, 약침치료 등… 하체 근육 및 관절 컨디션 유지를 위한 노력을 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46e1-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-334efe13d5b8\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46e0-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-15a4b5598c78\">30분 달리기에 도전하는데, 다리 아파서 포기하는 일은 없도록!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46e3-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-1dc5ce6ce2ce\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b46e2-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-397c86f58b17\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46e5-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-c5a0735bfd91\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46e4-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-c36a749d0ce8\">———————————————-</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46eb-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-1fb1d99eb777\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46ea-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-a1a4873b8515\">운동은 두뇌 신경을 자극합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46ed-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-0f9fe4a5bfc9\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46ec-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-393228a04496\">두뇌에 산소를 공급하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46f1-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-455a2865d0a4\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46f0-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-37045da86a38\">관절에 있는 고유감각수용체의 자극을 통해 뇌 신경을 자극하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46f3-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-df4dc97c5838\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46f2-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-7f983d42e4cf\">혈액순환 촉진을 통해 뇌로의 혈류량을 늘려줍니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46f7-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-0990ff0a7d5e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b46f6-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-8571360c0007\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46f9-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-2503f762e78d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b46f8-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-45eab0bd32d5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46fb-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-f37fcb6c70c8\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46fa-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-2d301f804af6\">뇌신경학을 연구하는 사람들은 운동을 통해 뇌신경 사이의 연결(시냅스)이 강화되고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b46ff-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-d5f15537c825\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b46fe-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-0b9aad584468\">뇌 신경 사이의 메세지를 전달하는 신경전달물질의 생성 및 분비, 그리고 신경물질의 작용이 강화되면서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b4702-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-ef2603881894\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b4700-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-bd874e6c5040\">뇌 기능이 좋아진다고 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b4705-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-07ee31cd065e\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b4704-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-d5ae9e5b3c0e\">더불어 ‘기분’이 좋아지고 우울감이 줄어든다고 하죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b4709-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-afd2ca7ce8ce\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b4708-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-1d74831cb7be\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b470b-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-1715a1e93b3e\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b470a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-dfba7a4a94e1\">가벼운 성취일지라도 성취감 두뇌와 감정에 큰 영향을 줍니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b470f-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-8591698fe728\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b470c-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-33472d760951\">성공 후 생기는 승리의 감정은 패배의식을 이겨낼 수 있게 해줍니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b4711-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-0dce1959f0cc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b4710-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-4db7d2bc638b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b4715-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-77bc582dbcb5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b4714-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-1baa6a82dd62\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b4719-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-53f59fdd5c95\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b4718-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-81ef438983a9\">—————————————</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b471b-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-2d2276905bb2\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b471a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-6d5bfbf0a56c\">환자분들에게도 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b471f-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-8332b1cb72d9\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b471e-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-bdde8cb61230\">운동을 하기를 종종 권합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b4723-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-89d15cb190d3\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b4722-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-850c97a989d7\">몸 상태에 맞춰, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b4727-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-437581957446\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b4726-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-a9a0f21ba836\">통증 정도에 맞춰</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e3b-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-59a5257583d4\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b6e3a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-6d2b6ba726b5\">가벼운 운동에서부터 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e3f-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-1b09a9086d77\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b6e3e-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-d10b6d4725f5\">힘든 운동까지 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e43-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-05892f88c68b\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b6e42-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-09d59e1eacf3\">자기에 맞는 운동을 찾아서 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e47-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-4f6a63e29139\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b6e46-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-0b7d5ddc8e47\">남은 인생동안 꾸준히 하기를 권하죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e4b-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-33a59a5086df\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b6e4a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-f9a04e2afae4\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e4f-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-b51f60849867\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b6e4e-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-8ddc774fdd7a\">통증이 심하지 않고, 적정한 운동을 할 수 있는 몸상태라면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e53-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-b73c01b8ab92\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b6e52-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-2393e9b87ea1\">숨이 가쁘게, 헉헉 대면서 가슴을 들썩일 정도의 강도로 운동하길 권합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e57-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-c5c955e2a3fd\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b6e55-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-c370a6b205a5\">얼마나 오래해야하는지는 당장은 중요하지 않습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e5b-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-37ecb1252fb7\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b6e5a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-379bdf905e61\">1-2분이라도 숨차고 헐떡이는 운동을 하시라 권하죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e60-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-adac3f61edd0\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b6e5e-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-491e485fd6ae\">- 그 이유는 나중에 다시 글을 써보도록 하겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e67-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-07e74566034a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b6e66-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-7f5a77b02384\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e69-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-03d178ea93c3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b6e68-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-b1af6bc454ed\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e6b-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-07d605d366e2\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b6e6a-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-07d2046ec8c3\">문원장이 30분 달리기에 성공하면,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e6d-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-2942e7306f9a\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b6e6c-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-add7df67effb\">그 후기를 다시 적어보도록 하겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e6f-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-ff4c85bc24ed\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b6e6e-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-ef0adaf3616d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e71-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-e3ea0fa61976\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-642b6e70-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-2dea42a0dc61\">모두 건강한 내일을 맞이하세요~ </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e73-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-f36ce2f2024c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b6e72-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-c756914d8506\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e75-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-7b8444326135\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b6e74-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-db1b6ffef59b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-642b6e77-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-1b41bd9ba92d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-642b6e76-c3d9-11ec-b1c8-8bf594ad6eb6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT 